query:
SELECT 
  a.id, a.name, 
  a.replacementValue,
  p.currentReplacementValue as pCRV,
  p.deferredMaintenanceCost as pDMC
FROM assets a
INNER JOIN projects p ON a.projectId = p.id
WHERE p.deletedAt IS NULL
LIMIT 5
